text:
I'm trying to load_translations like this, but the template_translations is always null on the live environment, but the same code works on the sandbox.

```{% set lang = request.query_dict.lflang %}
{% if lang %}
	{% set template_translations = load_translations("../_locales/", lang, "nl") %}
{% endif %}```
What could be the problem?

Here is how we dealt with the translation :
```{%- if request.query_dict.language %}
    {%- set html_lang = request.query_dict.language %}
{%- elif request.query_dict.hsLang %}
    {%- set html_lang = request.query_dict.hsLang %}
{%- elif (request.path|split("/")) is containing "en" %}
    {%- set html_lang = "en" %}
{%- elif (request.path|split("/")) is containing "fr" %}
    {%- set html_lang = "fr" %}
{%- else %}
    {%- set html_lang = ROOTLANG %}
{%- endif %}


{%- set i18nLang = html_lang|split("-") %}
{%- set i18nPath = "./i18n/" ~ i18nLang[0] ~ ".html" %}
{% import i18nPath as i18n %}```
